{"tid":1946260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推！]今日3月27號 發生咗咩事？","createTime":"2020-03-27T13:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T17:57:27.000Z","uid":305221,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0ccde5a7d6a38fa720536676c4682f412f85e6","tid":1946260,"uid":305221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"玩ig challenge嘅同時<br />\n望下<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日發生咗咩事</span></span> 對家一直冇停過手 我地又憑咩停??對唔對得住咁多手足??<br />\n求下大家唔好再做善忘嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得夜晚聽到有咩事就<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拎起部電話開cam開mic錄</span></span><br />\n記得<span style=\"color: red;\">大力懲罰黃店 </span>外賣自取等等仲有好多方法<br />\n記得搭巴士開<span style=\"color: red;\">airdrop share文宣</span><br />\n記得將電視較去<span style=\"color: red;\">港台/viu tv</span><br />\n記得<span style=\"color: red;\">CLS黃色youtuber</span><br />\n記得<span style=\"color: red;\">每日做Twitter任務</span><br />\n仲有好多 <br />\n但最重要嘅係記得保持個人衛生 <br />\n戴口罩勤洗手就真係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我保住條命 勿忘初衷 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係嘅話 你無資格自稱香港人。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDdrSoU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDdrSoU.jpg&h=041c36b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwijsXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwijsXf.jpg&h=73bd7fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kW7oUCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkW7oUCg.jpg&h=2333572c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5bXY3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5bXY3W.jpg&h=fdd